lattice

Class Lattice<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • lattice.Lattice<T>

  • public class Lattice<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Lattice Generic class. It carries the lattice value of TOP, BOTTOM or KNOWN (which corresponds to a particular value of the generic type)
